metadata.name: Magic Bath
metadata.description:
Birds are singing
 Their voice is drowned in the song of nature
There is no extra sound
Only the soothing sound of running water in the pond can be heard
 The smell of wet soil and jasmine flowers is everywhere

(This art is the dream of my mind so that you can feel and Smell my dream)

Life is short, enjoy it


Painting with: Procreate software
6300 * 7500 PX
